5271ef78bc04bcd97f7ae817575","tid":2240953,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"有些魔法書中規定魔杖長度必須等同於巫師的小臂，即從肘部至中指指尖，而其它魔法書中則規定魔杖長度必須為19英寸半，也有的說是21英寸。<br />\n<br />\n大部分魔杖都是筆直的，但也有例外。魔杖的末端可以是叉形或鑲嵌一顆水晶。有時，魔杖的末端必須鑲有各種魔法符號。很多情況下，魔杖的杆上雕刻有各種魔法咒語或魔符。"},{"pid":"368c731c2fb98b46923166560708e88e5fab1fb3","tid":2240953,"uid":157304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f20a8a7e7e6365271ef78bc04bcd97f7ae817575","tid":2240953,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"有些魔法書中規定魔杖長度必須等同於巫師的小臂，即從肘部至中指指尖，而其它魔法書中則規定魔杖長度必須為19英寸半，也有的說是21英寸。<br />\n<br />\n大部分魔杖都是筆直的，但也有例外。魔杖的末端可以是叉形或鑲嵌一顆水晶。有時，魔杖的末端必須鑲有各種魔法符號。很多情況下，魔杖的杆上雕刻有各種魔法咒語或魔符。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T04:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe09a1956303cb63aea9bd8e15e30aa306744a1","tid":2240953,"uid":228894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T04:47:47.000Z","msg":"處女膜還完咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe9b4aa98b5fe93219c283f6eea828313a727dc","tid":2240953,"uid":105176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T04:49:52.000Z","msg":"Cls po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2214ed875f756287c38c23a6b7827cc41e10e3ba","tid":2240953,"uid":173060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T04:52:11.000Z","msg":"影分身，3穴齊發又得，同時屌3條女都得"},{"pid":"08ab926d53bcc4af057deee645ab0dfc16790f9e","tid":2240953,"uid":157304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dfe9b4aa98b5fe93219c283f6eea828313a727dc","tid":2240953,"uid":105176,"like":0,"dislike